        <div class="hero-eyebrow">A patient&apos;s story through the operating model</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title">His consultant<br><em>still reads</em><br>the trend.</h1>
        <p class="hero-strap">Mark is 65. Diagnosed with low-risk prostate cancer and placed on active surveillance under Adam at the local trust. The quarterly PSA is supposed to be routine. The clinic trip to get it is anything but. <strong>This is the story of how the surveillance happens at home and the clinical accountability stays in clinic.</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-portrait-box">
        <div class="hero-portrait-circ">
          <img src="Assets/Personas/mark.png" alt="Mark">
        </div>
        <div class="hero-portrait-name">Mark</div>
